# Gitmoji commit — emoji first, then short English description
#
# ✨  New feature
# 🐛  Bug fix
# 📝  Documentation
# 📄  Config / .env.example
# 🌐  i18n / translations
# ♻️  Refactor
# ⚡  Performance
# 🔒  Security
# 👷  CI/CD / deploy
# 🔖  Release
# ⬆️  Upgrade dependencies
# 🎨  UI / styling
# 🗃️  Database
# 🔧  Tooling
#
# Examples:
# ✨ Add Hetzner server renewal flow
# 🐛 Fix subscription cron timezone
# 📝 Update README installation steps
